America, the Beast and the Devil's Deadly Mark - Part 1: The Beast on the Move - Part 1 of the sermon series "America, the Beast and the Devil's Deadly Mark". Steve Wohlberg reveals the identity of the beast of Revelation and how this power is actively working in the closing hours of Earth's history.
